environmental_stressor: Habitat conversion of overwintering forests to avocado plantations,
  combined with climate-shifted migration timing that left sanctuaries empty during
  traditional tourist season
family_situation: Widowed mother of two adult children who moved to Mexico City for
  work. Her son sends money but can't return - the sanctuary closed, no jobs remain.
  Her daughter calls weekly, begging her to leave, but Esperanza refuses to abandon
  the forest where four generations of women in her family learned to read the butterflies'
  ancient language.
